data.name: URINE BAGS - LUXUS TYPE
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Polyethylene (PE) Body
- DEHP-FREE PVC Tubing
- Polypropylene (PP) Clamps, Caps and Hangers

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- DEHP-FREE PVC
- Customized Printing
- T-Cross Outlet
- Double Hangers and Cords
- Ridged Universal Connector
- Needle and Needle free Sampling Port
- With and Without Sliding Clamp
- With and Without PASTEUR Chamber

## PERFORMANCE
- 2 Litters Capacity
- Non-Flow Return Valve
- Clear, flexible, kink-resistant inlet PVC tubing
- Highly Transparent
- Close system bag 2000ml with T valve outlet, with hook, with tie, filter, needle free sampling port, with drip chamber, tube O.D.: 10.0mm, length 110cm with sheet clamp and slide clamp.
